{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9824c1b63c","title":"宿迁沐阳大胜后集中主力好灭鲁南之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"32ac8b55f5","index":0,"year":1946,"month":12,"day":18,"articleId":"9824c1b63c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b342a1221e","type":"paragraph","text":"宿迁沐阳大胜后集中主力","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9824c1b63c"},{"id":"1a77fa56b7","type":"paragraph","text":"好灭鲁南之敌！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9824c1b63c"},{"id":"9c3988757b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年12月18日）陈、聚，并告张、邓，张、黎巴","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9824c1b63c"},{"id":"c49fbb5c37","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）庆祝宿沫前线大胜利，望对一切有功将士传令嘉奖（二）此战胜利整个苏鲁战局好转，游水暂失将来可以收复，也一定要收复。但第二步作战，似以集中主力外灭鲁南之敌，并相机收复枣峰台，使鲁南获得巩固，然后无顾虑地向南发展，逐步收复苏北、苏中一切失地。究应如何，望按实情处理","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9824c1b63c"},{"id":"eb13cf5d20","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9824c1b63c"},{"id":"25633d53ef","type":"paragraph","text":"玄巧[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给山东野战军司令员兼政治委员陈毅和华中野战军司令员栗裕的电报。2]张、邓，指张鼎丞、邓子恢，当时分别任华中军区司令员和政治委员。张、黎，指张云逸、黎玉，当时分别任山东军区第一副司令员和副政治委员。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9824c1b63c"}],"page":{"id":"933f1a939b","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"9824c1b63c","start":318,"end":318}}}},"__N_SSG":true}